entries.s_13: Everything worked out fine, thanks to you! You even saved my business. I can't thank you enough!
entries.s_24: I'm sorry, but we're not sending out tours today.
entries.s_25: I need to know about the group that disappeared 2 days ago.
entries.s_28: Ok. I have information from three spots. The trail leader radioed in at three spots along the trail. I'll give you those locations. Maybe you can find something there.
entries.s_29: Is there anything else that you can tell me?
entries.s_30: Just that I haven't heard anything since the third transmission.
entries.s_4: Please find out what happened to them.
